  m_Text: 'Build your camp, mine for ore, and craft items! Increase your camp''s
    value to rise up the tournament leaderboard and claim the first place!


    You
    will start a new camp. You will keep your chiefs, Exp, Gems, and runes.


    The
    tournament lasts two days. Rewards will be available for two days after the tournament
    ends.'
